{"tid":1806030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記住警暴要同港共政府掛勾，唔好俾人spin走風向","createTime":"2020-01-01T04:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T07:01:13.000Z","uid":310867,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5455ac2f33c43b32c7016f42e029577b4b9ef2e7","tid":1806030,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T04:42:32.000Z","msg":"幕後黑手係中共，最想香港人打香港人，唔用支國人出手，班狗只係被利用既condom，用完用盡即棄，唔好俾佢地用嚟spin走風向去開脫責任<br />\n<br />\n受訪記住追究警暴之餘，我要見到狙擊一班賣港奴才，賣港賊，主軸係中共文攻武嚇介入滲透，以時間換空間想拖死運動，港共不作為，政治問題武力解決先會令運動得以持續，港共繼續與民為敵，意圖民意逆轉搏翻盤，繼續藉著賣港去求榮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勿忘手足，尋求國際關注，繼續施加壓力<br />\n<br />\n1月1不插隊，準時入維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503e339695415837f592d4a7d69221e85f90bdef","tid":1806030,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4448d3ba74712c183dc372e3398e6d60ccb321ff","tid":1806030,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d525b8ce5fa8e7f208f3e1f4a4856eb78c6299fb","tid":1806030,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f4255cd18ff117002f6792d0a86cfe851f7105","tid":1806030,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1ae9b008b4ba09559de2d0a8a53c8362660441","tid":1806030,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T05:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8fd8ae5536a9a6d5c44d11f89f8d46bd48deeef","tid":1806030,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"